<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>MES 测试数据查询系统</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 40px; background-color: #f4f6f9; }
